Class TitleDeed

java.lang.Object
org.douggschwind.games.boardgames.monopoly.title.Title
org.douggschwind.games.boardgames.monopoly.title.TitleDeed
public class TitleDeed extends Title
An instance of this class is a property that can be owned, upon which houses and hotels may be built, and rent may be charged.
